title: The Sin of Lena Rivers (1932) PRE-CODE HOLLYWOOD

sources.title: The Sin of Lena Rivers (1932) PRE-CODE HOLLYWOOD
sources.description:
Stars: Charlotte Henry, Morgan Galloway, Beryl Mercer 
Director: Phil Rosen

Young Lena Rivers, who was born out of wedlock, goes to live with a rich uncle. Unfortunately, his wife and daughter make no secret of their dislike of her.
